          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1714736642578-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) into matchsticks</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your<strong> spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1714736655613-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1714736655613-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1714736655613-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1714736655613-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1714736655613-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped apple</strong>, <strong>grated carrot</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion </strong>to a bowl with your <strong>mayo </strong>and<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>white wine vinegar</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your<strong> slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
